Kharcha Hisab Diary – Terms of Service & Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 19 November 2025

1. Terms of Service
By using Kharcha Hisab Diary, you agree to the following:
- The app is for personal expense tracking only.
- All data (income, expenses, categories) is stored locally on your device.
- You are responsible for the data you enter.
- We may modify, suspend, or discontinue the app at any time without notice.
- You must be at least 13 years old to use this app (or have parental consent if under 18).
- Illegal use of the app is strictly prohibited.

2. Privacy Policy
We respect your privacy:
- Your expense data is stored only on your device and in your private Google Drive backup (if you enable sync).
- When you sign in with Google, we only access your name and email to identify your account.
- We do not collect, share, or sell any personal data to third parties.
- We do not use analytics or ads that track you.
- If you delete your account, all your data is permanently removed.
- Google Sign-In follows Google's Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy

3. Contact Us
If you have any questions, feel free to reach us at:
